OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772482267
OL,3,CRAF Cyprus site hit by drone hours
OL,4,Cafter Starmer allows US to use British
OL,5,Cbases
OL,7,FThe UK is drawing up plans to evacuate
OL,8,Fthousands of Brits from the Middle
OL,9,FEast, Good Morning Britain
OL,10,FCorrespondent Jay Akbar reports
OL,12,FA suspected drone strike hit RAF
OL,13,FAkrotiri in Cyprus after the prime
OL,14,Fminister gave the US permission to use
OL,15,Fthe site to attack Iranian missile
OL,16,Fpositions, the Ministry of Defence
OL,17,F(MoD) has confirmed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
