PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772482267
OL,3,CRAF Cyprus site hit by drone hours
OL,4,Cafter Starmer allows US to use British
OL,5,Cbases
OL,7,FThere were no casualties in the
OL,8,Fincident at the base near Limassol in
OL,9,Fthe early hours of Monday, but the
OL,10,FSovereign Base Areas Administration
OL,11,Fsaid "a temporary dispersal" was being
OL,12,Fplanned for non-essential personnel.
OL,14,FAn MoD spokesperson said: "Our armed
OL,15,Fforces are responding to a suspected
OL,16,Fdrone strike at RAF Akrotiri in Cyprus
OL,17,Fat midnight local time.
OL,19,F"Our force protection in the region is
OL,20,Fat the highest level and the base has
OL,21,Fresponded to defend our people.
OL,26,@sD@FOUsD@\O]vD@[OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
