OL,3,CRAF Cyprus site hit by drone hours
OL,4,Cafter Starmer allows US to use British
OL,5,Cbases
OL,7,F"This is a live situation and further
OL,8,Finformation will be provided in due
OL,9,Fcourse."
OL,11,FKonstantinos Letymbiotis, a Cyprus
OL,12,Fgovernment spokesman, said in a
OL,13,Fstatement on X only "limited" damage
OL,14,Fwas caused.
OL,16,FIn an earlier statement, people living
OL,17,Fin Akrotiri village had been advised
OL,18,Fto "shelter in place".
