OL,3,CRAF Cyprus site hit by drone hours
OL,4,Cafter Starmer allows US to use British
OL,5,Cbases
OL,7,FAccording to the MoD's website, the
OL,8,Fjoint operating base is "used as a
OL,9,Fforward mounting base for overseas
OL,10,Foperations in the Middle East and for
OL,11,Ffast jet training".
OL,13,FIt is understood that the UK
OL,14,Fgovernment has recently deployed
OL,15,Fadditional resources to bases in
OL,16,FCyprus as part of its ongoing
OL,17,Foperations in the Middle East.
OL,26,@pD@YOUsD@RO]
