OL,3,CRAF Cyprus site hit by drone hours
OL,4,Cafter Starmer allows US to use British
OL,5,Cbases
OL,7,FThe strike came hours after Keir
OL,8,FStarmer said the UK had allowed the US
OL,9,Fto strike Iranian missile sites from
OL,10,FBritish bases as officials plan an
OL,11,Funprecedented rescue operation for UK
OL,12,Fcitizens in the Gulf.
OL,14,FHostilities in the Middle East are
OL,15,Fentering their third day, with the US
OL,16,Fand Israel continuing to strike Iran
OL,17,Ffollowing the death of Supreme Leader
OL,18,FAyatollah Ali Khamenei in the initial
OL,19,Fattack on Saturday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
