OL,3,CRAF Cyprus site hit by drone hours
OL,4,Cafter Starmer allows US to use British
OL,5,Cbases
OL,7,FTensions in the region continued
OL,8,Fovernight on Monday, with Israel
OL,9,Flaunching strikes on Lebanon's
OL,10,Fcapital, Beirut, after Hezbollah fired
OL,11,Fmissiles across the border.
OL,13,FMore than 200,000 British nationals,
OL,14,Fincluding military personnel, are
OL,15,Fthought to be at risk in the Gulf as
OL,16,Fthe Tehran regime launches further
OL,17,Fmissiles at its neighbours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
