PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772482267
OL,3,CRAF Cyprus site hit by drone hours
OL,4,Cafter Starmer allows US to use British
OL,5,Cbases
OL,7,FLate on Sunday, the prime minister
OL,8,Fsaid he had agreed to a US request to
OL,9,Fuse British bases to protect UK
OL,10,Fnationals and allies in the region,
OL,11,Faccusing Iran of pursuing a "scorched
OL,12,Fearth strategy".
OL,14,FStarmer said British forces would not
OL,15,Fbe directly involved in the strikes,
OL,16,Fand the bases would only be used for
OL,17,Fthe "specific and limited defensive
OL,18,Fpurpose" of targeting missile storage
OL,19,Fdepots and launchers being used to
OL,20,Fattack Iran's neighbours.
OL,26,@sD@]OUtD@OO]yD@EOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
