OL,3,CRAF Cyprus site hit by drone hours
OL,4,Cafter Starmer allows US to use British
OL,5,Cbases
OL,7,FHe said: "We have taken the decision
OL,8,Fto accept this request ` to prevent
OL,9,FIran firing missiles across the
OL,10,Fregion, killing innocent civilians,
OL,11,Fputting British lives at risk, and
OL,12,Fhitting countries that have not been
OL,13,Finvolved."
OL,15,FIt is not clear which bases will be
OL,16,Fused, but Donald Trump has previously
OL,17,Freferred to asking to use Diego
OL,18,FGarcia, one of the Chagos Islands in
OL,19,Fthe Indian Ocean.
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
