PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772482267
OL,3,CRAF Cyprus site hit by drone hours
OL,4,Cafter Starmer allows US to use British
OL,5,Cbases
OL,7,FReports have also suggested the US
OL,8,Fcould use RAF Fairford in
OL,9,FGloucestershire, which can handle
OL,10,FAmerican heavy bombers.
OL,12,FStarmer's decision followed a day of
OL,13,Fconversations with regional leaders,
OL,14,Fduring which it is understood they
OL,15,Fasked the UK to do more to protect
OL,16,Fthem from Iranian missiles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
