OL,3,CRAF Cyprus site hit by drone hours
OL,4,Cafter Starmer allows US to use British
OL,5,Cbases
OL,7,FThe prime minister insisted the
OL,8,Fdecision was fully in line with
OL,9,Finternational law, and the government
OL,10,Fhas published a summary of its legal
OL,11,Fposition setting out that it is acting
OL,12,Fin "collective self-defence".
OL,14,FThe UK will also continue to carry out
OL,15,Fthe defensive operations that have
OL,16,Fengaged British forces in shooting
OL,17,Fdown Iranian drones threatening
OL,18,Fnorthern Iraq and Qatar.
OL,26,@tD@DOUtD@\O]
